# Web Dashboard Rules
- Next.js 14 App Router. Use Server Components where possible.
- UI: Shadcn/ui from @trendywheels/ui-web + Tailwind with @trendywheels/ui-tokens preset.
- Charts: Recharts only.
- State: TanStack Query (server), Zustand (client).
- RBAC enforced both server-side (API) and client-side (route guards).
- Lighthouse ≥90 target.
